text: Franjo Jurjević (born 22 November 1932) is a Croatian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bjelovar
